  Fix deps (#504134 by Matthew Schultz and Eternal Sorrow)

  18 Jul 2014; Pacho Ramos <pacho@gentoo.org> -virtualgl-2.3.2-r3.ebuild,
  virtualgl-2.3.3.ebuild:
  amd64 stable, bug #508136; drop old

  18 Jun 2014; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> virtualgl-2.3.2-r3.ebuild,
  virtualgl-2.3.3.ebuild:
  Update dependencies to require guaranteed EAPI=5 or multilib ebuilds, bug
  #513718.

  14 Jun 2014; Pawel Hajdan jr <phajdan.jr@gentoo.org> virtualgl-2.3.3.ebuild:
  x86 stable wrt bug #508136

  26 Jan 2014; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> virtualgl-2.3.2-r3.ebuild:
  Stable for x86, wrt bug #480128

